This '''list of tallest buildings in Dubai''' ranks skyscrapers in the city of [[Dubai]] by height. Dubai is the most populous city of the [[United Arab Emirates]]. Dubai has 58 buildings that stand taller than 200 metres (656 ft), which is more than any other city in the world surpassing [[Hong Kong]], and [[New York City]]. It has 76 buildings that stand taller than 180 metres (591 ft). However, Dubai has 14 highrises whose height exceeds 300 metres (984 ft); which is more than any other city in the world, in comparison, Hong Kong and Chicago have only six and New York has 4.
